<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='643000' id='t-643000'>I'll give you two different ways to think about this problem that are the beginning</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='649000' id='t-649000'>of my thinking about how to think about it.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='651000' id='t-651000'>But what we need is not just a few oddballs like me thinking about this.</span>
