<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='806000' id='t-806000'>But there is a problem with that view.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='808000' id='t-808000'>And the problem is the following:</span>
